gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Timberwolves 110, Nuggets 89
gameRecap.excerpt: The Timberwolves defeated the Nuggets, 110-89. Anthony Edwards recorded a team-high 24 points for the Timberwolves, while Karl-Anthony Towns added 21 points, 8 rebounds and 4 assists in the victory. Nikola Jokic tallied 25 points, 10 rebounds and 3 assists for the Nuggets in the losing effort. The Timberwolves improve to 2-2 on the season, while the Nuggets fall to 4-1.
